translated: Lekänder, Ossian Hugo, bank director, Ljungby, b. 11/5/85 in Karlskrona of unknown occupation. S/o H. Lekänder and Amy Sandholm. Married for 13 years to Hanna Pettersson. Children: Birgit b. 15, Lars-Olof b. 17, Gunnar b. 23. — Assistant at the County Chancellery Office from 1905-1907, civil servant at Småland Private Bank in Ljungby from 1907-1913, cashier from 1913 and currently CEO of Sunnerbo Hds Savings Bank in Ljungby, serving on the board since 1938. Vice chairman of the local board for a secondary school and chairman of the building commission. Wrote: Sunnerbo Hds Savings Bank 1863-1938. Hobby: sport fishing. Military rank: Patriotic Ground Forces Major.
